    "description": "Not just a lobby. A first impression that lasts.\n\nA clubhouse lobby layered with warm teak wood finishes and subtle groove detailing, balanced with full-body tiles that extend from the floor to half the wall ensuring durability in a high-traffic space.\n\nAs you move through, the space unfolds into a double-height volume anchored by a statement chandelier and a large mirror that enhances depth, light, and a subtle touch of glamour.\n\nThe lower lobby is kept minimal, with clean lines and walls finished in a warm beige tone, complemented by rust-red seating. A modern chandelier and abstract artwork complete the space, adding character without overwhelming it.\n\nPhotography by @_yashrjain \n\n#interiordesign #lobby #clubhouse #design",
